\c 5
\p
\v 1 Zvino zvakaitika pazuva retatu kuti Esiteri wakapfeka \add nguvo\add* dzeuhosi\x + 4.16.\x*, ndokumira pachivanze chemukati cheimba yamambo, pakatarisana neimba yamambo; mambo waiva agere pachigaro cheushe cheumambo hwake muimba yeumambo, pakatarisana nemukova weimba\x + 4.11. 6.4.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino zvakaitika mambo paakaona Esiteri vahosi vamambo amire pachivanze, wakawana nyasha pameso ake\x + 2.9.\x*; mambo ndokutandavadzira Esiteri tsvimbo yeushe yegoridhe yaiva muruoko rwake. Esiteri ndokuswedera, ndokubata musoro wetsvimbo\x + 4.11. 8.4.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino mambo wakati kwaari: Unei, vahosi Esiteri? Uye chikumbiro chako chii? Uchachipiwa, kunyange kusvika pahafu yeushe\x + 5.6. 7.2. Mako 6.23.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Esiteri wakati: Kana zvakanaka kuna mambo, mambo naHamani ngavauye nhasi kumabiko andakamugadzirira.
\v 5 Zvino mambo wakati: Kurumidzisai Hamani, kuti aite shoko raEsiteri. Naizvozvo vakauya mambo naHamani kumabiko Esiteri aaiva aita.
\p
\v 6 Zvino mambo wakati kuna Esiteri pamabiko ewaini\x + 7.2.\x*: Chikumbiro chako chii? Zvino uchachipiwa. Uye chii chishuvo chenyu\x + 5.3. 7.2. 9.12.\x*? Zvichaitwa kunyange kusvika pahafu yeushe\x + 5.6. 7.2. Mako 6.23.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino Esiteri wakapindura ndokuti: Chikumbiro changu nechishuvo changu \add ndeichi\add*:
\v 8 Kana ndawana nyasha pameso amambo, uye kana zvakanaka kuna mambo kupa chikumbiro changu, nekuita chishuvo changu, mambo naHamani ngavauye pamabiko andichavaitira; zvino mangwana ndichaita zvinoenderana neshoko ramambo\x + 8.5. 7.3. Gen.. 18.3. 30.27.\x*.
\s Hamani anoronga kuuraya Modhekai
\p
\v 9 Zvino Hamani wakabuda nezuva iro nemufaro, nemoyo wakanaka\x + 1 Madz. 8.66.\x*; asi Hamani paakaona Modhekai pasuwo ramambo, kuti haana kusimuka, uye kuti kumudederera, Hamani wakazara nehasha nekuda kwaModhekai\x + 3.5.\x*.
\v 10 Asi Hamani wakazvidzora; paakasvika muimba yake, wakatuma ndokupinza shamwari dzake\x + Gen.. 45.1.\x*, naZereshi mukadzi wake\x + 5.14. 6.13.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Hamani akavarondedzera kubwinya kwefuma yake, nekuwanda kwevana vake\x + 9.7-10.\x*, nezvese mambo zvaakamukwiridzira pazviri\x + 3.1.\x*, uye kuti wakamusimudzira pamusoro pemachinda nevaranda vamambo\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 12 Hamani ndokuti: Hongu, Esiteri vahosi vamambo havana kupinza munhu pamwe namambo pamabiko aaita kunze kwangu; uye namangwana ndakokwa kwaari, pamwe namambo\x + 1 Sam. 9.13. 1 Sam. 9.24. 2 Sam. 13.23. Job. 1.4.\x*.
\v 13 Asi zvese hazvindifadzi panguva yose yandinoona Modhekai muJudha agere pasuwo ramambo.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Zereshi mukadzi wake neshamwari dzake dzose vakati kwaari: Ngakuitwe danda remakubhiti makumi mashanu kureba, zvino mangwana taurai kuna mambo kuti Modhekai aremberedzwe pariri. Zvino pindai makafara namambo pamabiko. Zvino nyaya iyi yaiva yakanaka pamberi paHamani. Zvino akaita danda\x + 5.14. 6.13.\x*.